# Current Task File Standard

- Keep required sections from `SCHEMA.md`.
- Keep metadata and `task_contract` aligned with actual status.
- Keep dependencies explicit and update revision when scope changes.
- Maintain concise, testable AC statements.
- Keep AC -> test mapping specific (class/method or command-level evidence).
